Now, lege lorde of my lyf, leue I yow ask;
546			2	3	-	e knowe þe cost of þis cace, kepe I no more
547			2	3	-	To telle yow tene3 þer-of neuer bot trifel;
548		D	2	3	-	Bot I am boun to þe bur barely to morne,
549			2	3	-	To sech þe gome of þe grene, as god wyl me wysse.

3e ar a sleper vn-sly3e, þat mon may slyde hider;
