For hit is symple in hit-self. & so hit wel seme3?
1848			3	29	-	Lo! so hit is littel, & lasse hit is worþy;
1849		B	3	29	-	Bot who-so knew þe costes þat knit ar þer-inne,
1850			3	29	-	He wolde hit prayse at more prys, parauenture;
1851		C	3	29	-	For quat gome so is gorde with þis grene lace,
1852			3	29	-	While he hit hade hemely halched aboute,
1853			3	29	-	Þer is no haþel vnder heuen to-hewe hym þat my3t;
1854		D	3	29	-	For he my3t not he slayn, for sly3t vpon erþe.

Wheþer þis be þe grene chapelle;
